bPVd-XfRiS6JwsgqL83XXO1Car_AvIi9SC5XF3Xb8Q/80KxeFeeTkU5VGg3iD3uK2QKpI7dhJGd/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="斯洛文尼亚总理在有史以来最接近的投票中击败特朗普盟友"&gt;扼杀&lt;/a&gt;，而在西班牙，总理佩德罗·桑切斯的社会党&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/zpCVT2EWbOQ20xX2u3ctU05eJhOADyWYFIOVXeu5-BG5LPtlmVscav82E9AAfkKI35vDC9A1wNo1vKNjPN50x0_HX3tnHtYANZQHn0Y6WMSeZV-ZRKUsy6JqHIdMT5JqJ_6h1uuACYCJR1o09C583ADZyWfj48sHD99Isw-A4Brz5uIOJbo29dkXSaXlXVQNeW0eJnrjGLXg0hUjsePg2WhnWh_bgdPVovelxboN9AnKda4hYX1q8zmAgzvBwb6plQhrv1TRYogHWa8YnV-SPkWiLhbqVh7aGdZ_7ykhelqOCMeOAbC2aJHbeJbXqmORlSd4534KeJeDXIvcWT6gZEY_Tul0VCgAKhs2r72ovXujlVHM1zQ98HWe6Zjno1oO-QMU6A8h3CwSLraJCV-SzpvTdGgp6m15GnzwK6i4-rVY32WSAp-X5ImD58iOCYkRPcKfVaeQOQU-nS7WceBCSOvprsm4fl5XpPuFxVTb0ef2aywYygBAmJ01NYXBm6uUcAsFATiwnoll7OC_KLApVIU/ybEEvEPcnl6FlSFzKQlCcnejL0pIz0vx/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="西班牙极右翼动摇，桑切斯社会主义者声称扭转局面"&gt;出人意料地卷土重来，挫败了极右翼的崛起&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;与此同时，奈杰尔·法拉奇在英国的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/YQwWUarMMmsdIJsFk-mypwPefE7lcmhfsUQ8vE6T0SijH1YvmEywtOH09OAmNK0YKJT10bJndE-M2uUtz4Sb280Sds5_1ivMwTNdGYTAZbs1veTeD_SnzRpjSwCw6QCAOohDFuCtj-WHaI9Eg5mZ_v5pM8n5Es6obbchdyPUzTi5iNpfbTOGdh2ivUL6cqwCQG4rOxHw9MZj2KzQSigwsNioWYKRkMDJFh_HHhYldZF-ZeIyVPQAjEFLTKbRioQ0V6jAFfLq-LFJBAZj9wJKK6bIgccTS4Wn4a6WIc_o1R6Zqp5aE_72fLxrCv92u2eBG6v7UKScsBXiRDcSjDBGI6EEznecahV_TP6jXlg69kuGWnbG3nd71eEnDc2HRgnrAaQ1paHlKWEhrWxspnbdaswArcJZW6f-WKbKMFdlvr-1ID87Cog_UUjqSe7dshjKEt3a7JUFaq5eLVvwsj50YNPd2sL_oAflysddogEj8wmj70KJH26ut84ZRwNYamyN-Qmt-5Y0diEldHO7Gw/MUkTBZ6mZDWphMqyiNaDB1bj9w1peoMf/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="新的英国极右翼政党即将争夺法拉奇的选民"&gt;民调中失去了光泽&lt;/a&gt;。他是英国脱欧运动的策划者，该运动赢得了公投——这是民粹主义者传统上青睐的工具，直到他们出了差错。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;接下来是维克托·欧尔班，一位保守的民族主义者，他将匈牙利变成了一个不自由的国家。尽管他牢牢掌握权力，但